race.description: Australia Day Long Wknd Raceday 25th Jan Handicap
race.comment: Tough. LISSARO (14) has been racing in stronger and measure up his chances on his nose defeat at the Gold Coast two starts back. May have to do it the hard way again, but finds the right race. SECURITY ADVISOR (1) had no luck at Kilcoy last time but won there this grade prior as a firm favourite. Needs a good ride, but the 3kg claim brings him right into it. ANOTHER DAZZLER (6) is hard to catch but has pieces of form that would see him in the finish. Maps well and sits down in the weights. BUDDY'S TALE (10) is another good enough on his day. Carries a feather with the 3kg claim and should be around the mark.
